Ask HN: What's Your Experience with Pioneer.app?
text:
If you haven't heard of it before, Pioneer.app is an accelerator with a tournament-style selection system. Startups compete by submitting weekly updates, which are ranked by other startup founders. There's an ELO-like points system.

Wondering:

Do you know anyone who has been selected for the accelerator program?

How's the "product quality" of the accelerator program?

If you've been through ANY accelerator before, would you repeat the experience even if you could build and MVP and raise a seed round yourself?

Ask HN: Snapsearch for All Your Documents
text:
Have you ever had the issue where you can't remember where you kept a certain file or document. Wether it was on your Google drive, or maybe in your one drive, dropbox, or maybe even your trash?

What if there was a website, desktop app and mobile app wherein you just had to link your various cloud provider accounts to the app once and you can search all your files on all your cloud providers!

Later on, i would also like to add image recognition to this so you can search for images across various providers.

Does this solution sound like something you'd be willing to try?
